  <summary>De-squeeze anamorphic footage</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Get that cinematic look from your video without opening a heavyweight editor. Anamorph de-squeezes anamorphic video shot with an anamorphic lens on a 16:9 sensor, like the one in your smartphone. Perfect for the Moment Anamorphic lens or other lenses designed for Pixel, Galaxy, iPhone, etc.</p>
